---
title: Herby Dijon Turkey Scallopine on Savoury Mushroom Rice
description: This is not your average turkey dinner. Foraged flavours of hearty mushrooms, savoury gravy and hearty herbs, make this turkey dinner oh-so-cozy. Now that’s a weeknight win!
